Question: In one image two people can be seen working on a thatched roof.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/J4vDNphqnYQ/maxresdefault.jpg

Right image URL: http://thatchinginfo.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/29b1.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many people are working on the thatched roof?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many people are working on the thatched roof?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} + {ANSWER1} == 2')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
